msgstr "ສະແດງຕົວຊີ້ບອກ&ແຖບ:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, chkShowTabs)
#: dialogs/textareaappearanceconfigwidget.ui:176
#, kde-format
